exam_title: AWS Certified Cloud Practitioner Practice Exam 5

wrong_answers.question: Which of the following allows you to categorize and track your AWS costs on a detailed level?
What is the best type of instance purchasing option to choose if you will run an EC2 instance for 3 months to perform a job that is uninterruptible?
How can your RDS production instances be more cost-effective when they will be used for a long period of time?
wrong_answers.your_answer: You can stop your RDS instances when idle to prevent AWS from charging you during this time
wrong_answers.correct_answer: You can request reserved instances to get discounts on your instance costs
